sentences: Harald Sokal (born 18 March 1954) is an Austrian jazz saxophonist.
Between 1977 and 1985, he performed with his own band "Timeless", and joined the Vienna Art Orchestra in 1977, in which he played, except for a four-year break, until he left in 2010.
